0, "final": 56600, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 566"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "3", "description": "角色扮演"}, {"id": "70", "description": "搶先體驗"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 8 月 21 日"}}}}, "us": {"1943730": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Wicked Island", "steam_appid": 1943730, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to Wicked Island</strong>, a harsh but deeply alluring open-world survival game where your combat skills and your deepest desires collide. Scavenge for resources, build a fortified home, and craft powerful gear to survive a wilderness teeming with ferocious and highly aggressive monsters. Whether you are taming a pack of loyal beasts, taking to the skies on the back of a dragon, or succumbing to the island's more explicit temptations, your fate, and your body, is in your hands. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/44bce89fda772a9ffd2b93c776f651d9.avif?t=1773223163\" width=800 height=78 /></span>Bring your ideal fantasy to life with an in-depth character creator. Fully customize your body and appearance to your exact preferences before venturing out into the wild. But tread carefully—if you fall to the island's roaming predators, a fully integrated sex-defeat system ensures they will claim their ultimate prize.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/40f10e787ba94d6fde36cce7810eba53.poster.avif?t=1773223163\" width=506 height=900 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/40f10e787ba94d6fde36cce7810eba53.webm?t=1773223163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/40f10e787ba94d6fde36cce7810eba53.mp4?t=1773223163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/27123f8c64edfedb9efe14c3efff15ce.avif?t=1773223163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras_big/27123f8c64edfedb9efe14c3efff15ce.avif?t=1773223163 width=800 height=57 /></span>Gather resources across diverse biomes to construct your dream base anywhere in the world. Craft the weapons, armor, and tools you need to survive the elements and conquer dangerous dungeons, caves, and ancient ruins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/9df67d2d88465348f7c3bd5381b84819.poster.avif?t=1773223163\" width=800 height=642 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/9df67d2d88465348f7c3bd5381b84819.webm?t=1773223163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/9df67d2d88465348f7c3bd5381b84819.mp4?t=1773223163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/b7e4421eb59cfb3303a55dc83fa74500.poster.avif?t=1773223163\" width=698 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/b7e4421eb59cfb3303a55dc83fa74500.webm?t=1773223163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/b7e4421eb59cfb3303a55dc83fa74500.mp4?t=1773223163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shape Your World</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Extensive Customization:</strong> Fully customize your character's body and appearance to fit your exact desires.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Base Building:</strong> Gather resources to construct your own custom home and defenses anywhere on the map.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Deep Crafting:</strong> Forage, mine, and craft essential survival gear, weapons, and tools.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Living Open World:</strong> Explore diverse biomes featuring deep caves, forgotten ruins, and challenging dungeons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dynamic Environment:</strong> Experience a fully realized day/night cycle and dynamic weather effects that impact gameplay—beware of ambushes while you sleep!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combat &amp; Taming</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Beast Mastery:</strong> Gather, tame, and command a pack of creatures that will follow you and fight for you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dragon Riding:</strong> Dominate the skies and rain fire down upon your enemies from dragon-back.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Action-Based Combat:</strong> Engage in fast-paced, skill-based fights against a massive variety of creatures.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unrestricted Adult Content (18+)</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Losing has Consequences:</strong> An optional Sex Defeat system where monsters take what they want if you fall in battle.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explicit Encounters:</strong> Highly detailed sex animations featuring a wide variety of different monsters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Breeding Mechanics:</strong> Rescue slaves and breed them with your tamed creatures.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Extreme Kinks:</strong> Optional toggles for pregnancy (featuring explicit birth scenes) and cum inflation.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/032b552e334af408fea03a8ae48817f0.avif?t=1773223163\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras_big/032b552e334af408fea03a8ae48817f0.avif?t=1773223163 width=800 height=65 /></span>You don't have to survive alone. Tame wild creatures to build a loyal pack that fights by your side, rescue captives to breed with your monsters, or take to the skies and immolate your enemies from the back of a massive dragon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/433ac9f6193ff2cb7ea727e6993a143b.poster.avif?t=1773223163\" width=554 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/433ac9f6193ff2cb7ea727e6993a143b.webm?t=1773223163\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943730/extras/433ac9f6193ff2cb7ea727e6993a143b.mp4?t=1773223163\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_para